'''Nexus Player'''是由[[谷歌|谷歌]]和[[华硕|华硕]]共同开发的{{le|数字媒体播放器|Digital media player}}，是第二个[[Google_Nexus|Google Nexus]]系列消费类设备中的媒体播放器。搭载[[Android_Lollipop|Android 5.0（“Lollipop”）]][[操作系统|操作系统]]，其将是采用[[Android_TV|Android TV]]电视平台的第一个设备。Nexus Player支持Google Cast，该功能在电视上选择和控制媒体播放，并且首先在[[Chromecast|Chromecast]]上推出。

==发布==
Nexus Player在2014年11月3日发布，两天后在[[Google_Play|Google Play]]商店以99美元供预购<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.androidcentral.com/nexus-9-now-available-pre-order-google-play|title=Nexus 6, 9 and Player arrive in Google Play, orders live for 9 and Player|work=Android Central|first=Andrew|last=Martonik|date=October 17, 2014|accessdate=October 17, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150129085033/http://www.androidcentral.com/nexus-9-now-available-pre-order-google-play|archive-date=2015-01-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，後來在美國的零售商店可供購買<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.androidpolice.com/2015/01/25/the-nexus-player-is-now-available-at-us-retailers-best-buy-newegg-and-amazon|title=The Nexus Player Is Now Available At US Retailers: Best Buy, Newegg, And Amazon|publisher=Android Police|date=January 25, 2015|accessdate=January 26, 2015|archive-date=2019-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191018221304/https://www.androidpolice.com/2015/01/26/the-nexus-player-is-now-available-at-us-retailers-best-buy-newegg-and-amazon/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==硬件==
它有一個1.8[[赫兹|GHz]]四核[[英特爾Atom|英特爾Atom]][[處理器|處理器]]與1[[Gibibyte|GB]]的[[随机存取存储器|RAM]]和8GB內部存儲<ref>{{cite web|title=Nexus Player|url=http://www.google.com/nexus/player/|website=Google|publisher=Google Inc.|accessdate=16 October 2014|archive-date=2016-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160318025404/https://www.google.com/nexus/player/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

